channel.title: Chosen Pkz 459
channel.description:
[i]Hey everyone, i thought i would show off a little of my latest project. This is a highly edit Dynastly Base, mixed partially with BattleScape. I added a lot of cool features check it out! [/i]
[b]Server Features[/b] [i]-95% Clan Chat, still making player able to toggle CC settings. -All skills working, add 100% summoning, and 40% Construction. Still working on construction maps. -Real Runescape Genie random event, you receive a lamp that grants you xp in you choice (If you Don't talk to genie teleported away. -Never Before seen training areas & Miningames. -3 Anti Dupe method, thanks to moparscape tutorials(: -SYI & anti Nuller.[/i]
[b]Minigames[/b] -[i]Barrows 100% like runescape full finished as of today -Duel Arena -Pest Control 75% -Hord Minigame 55% -Fight Caves -Jad (20 Waves) -Working on real godwars, loading RS GW's map![/i] --------------------- [b]Player vs Monster[/b] [i]-Npc's freeze you! & You can freeze Npc's! -Multi target spells Example : (Ice Barrage). -Lunar Spells work on Npc's. (Vengeance). -Battlscape PvM combat, spec right perfect like RS. -Npc Defense, i noticed most server's don't have correct Npc defense bonuses. -Npc attack rate, is perfect.. every Npc has a chance of hitting on you. 75% like runescape. -Certain Npc's can teleblock.[/i]
[b]Player vs Player[/b] [i]-Magic & Range following! -Mutli spells in Mutli zones. -All lunar, Modern, Ancient Magic! -Every 3 steps is Wildy Level. -All dragon weapon special attacl 100%. -Perfectly timed spell delays. -And a lot more! [/i] [b]Emote System[/b] [i]-Vengeance & Vengeance other. -Defender block & Crossbow, Karils emotes. -GS Specials, attacks, block, run. -525 Dragon Claw emote. -New 562 whip emote, you can toggle on or off, with new whip look!
[b]Pictures[/b] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/izsrbk.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/wsmpzr.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2hp5bt5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/6gg1hy.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/fwiog6.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/v3q3rk.jpg[/img] I'll be adding a few more pictures over time, so let me know what you think!

item.title: Chosen Pkz 459
item.dc:creator: @Chosen_Pkz Chosen Pkz
item.description:
@Chosen_Pkz wrote:

Hey everyone, i thought i would show off a little of my latest project. This is a highly edit Dynastly Base, mixed partially with BattleScape. I added a lot of cool features check it out!

Server Features
-95% Clan Chat, still making player able to toggle CC settings.
-All skills working, add 100% summoning, and 40% Construction. Still working on construction maps.
-Real Runescape Genie random event, you receive a lamp that grants you xp in you choice (If you Don’t talk to genie teleported away.
-Never Before seen training areas & Miningames.
-3 Anti Dupe method, thanks to moparscape tutorials(:
-SYI & anti Nuller.

Minigames
-Barrows 100% like runescape full finished as of today
-Duel Arena
-Pest Control 75%
-Hord Minigame 55%
-Fight Caves
-Jad (20 Waves)
-Working on real godwars, loading RS GW’s map!

Player vs Monster
-Npc’s freeze you! & You can freeze Npc’s!
-Multi target spells Example : (Ice Barrage).
-Lunar Spells work on Npc’s. (Vengeance).
-Battlscape PvM combat, spec right perfect like RS.
-Npc Defense, i noticed most server’s don’t have correct Npc defense bonuses.
-Npc attack rate, is perfect… every Npc has a chance of hitting on you. 75% like runescape.
-Certain Npc’s can teleblock.

Player vs Player
-Magic & Range following!
-Mutli spells in Mutli zones.
-All lunar, Modern, Ancient Magic!
-Every 3 steps is Wildy Level.
-All dragon weapon special attacl 100%.
-Perfectly timed spell delays.
-And a lot more!

Emote System
[i]-Vengeance & Vengeance other.
-Defender block & Crossbow, Karils emotes.
-GS Specials, attacks, block, run.
-525 Dragon Claw emote.
-New 562 whip emote, you can toggle on or off, with new whip look!
